        "custom_liquid": "{{ 'movaro-product.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}{{ 'movaro-product.js' | asset_url | script_tag }}\n<div class=\"mvb bg-paper\"><div class=\"mvb-sec ab-d\"><div class=\"eyebrow reveal\">The nightmare you know too well<\/div>\n    <h2 class=\"lead-h reveal\">Nail day shouldn't feel like a war.<\/h2>\n    <p class=\"lead-p reveal\">The hiss. The claws drawing blood. The two-person wrestling match that ends with your cat under the bed and you giving up — again. Eventually you just book the $150 sedated trim and feel guilty about all of it.<\/p>\n    <p class=\"lead-p reveal\" style=\"margin-top:15px\">Here's what nobody tells you: <b class=\"hl\">your cat isn't being bad — it's scared.<\/b> And a scared cat doesn't need to be fought. It needs to feel safe. That's the whole idea behind the wrap.<\/p>\n\n    <div class=\"ill tape reveal\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'movaro-hotspot.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=760\" srcset=\"{{ 'movaro-hotspot.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=400 400w, {{ 'movaro-hotspot.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=760 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width:540px) 90vw, 480px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Movaro wrap on a calm cat\">\n      <span class=\"chip\" style=\"top:14px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%)\">👆 Tap the + dots to see how it works<\/span>\n      <button class=\"hotspot\" style=\"top:56%;left:44%\" aria-label=\"pressure\">+<span class=\"tip\">😌 Even, gentle pressure — most cats settle in ~60s<\/span><\/button>\n      <button class=\"hotspot\" style=\"top:42%;left:58%\" aria-label=\"velcro\">+<span class=\"tip\">🐾 Velcro opens one limb at a time<\/span><\/button>\n      <button class=\"hotspot\" style=\"top:72%;left:32%\" aria-label=\"fabric\">+<span class=\"tip\">🤫 Soft, quiet fabric — no plastic crinkle<\/span><\/button>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"brow reveal\">\n      <div class=\"ill\"><img src=\"{{ 'movaro-about.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=320\" srcset=\"{{ 'movaro-about.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=160 160w, {{ 'movaro-about.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=320 320w\" sizes=\"150px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Calm cat in the Movaro wrap\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"bt\"><h3>Calm, not trapped<\/h3>\n        <p>A $15 bag just traps a cat — which makes the panic worse. The Movaro wrap works the opposite way: even, gentle swaddle pressure (the same principle that calms a swaddled baby) tells your cat's nervous system it's safe. Within about a minute, <b class=\"hlw\">most cats stop fighting and settle.<\/b> Then velcro flaps open <i>one limb at a time<\/i>.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"proof\">● Works for nails, meds, subQ fluids &amp; ears<\/span><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"brow reveal\">\n      <div class=\"ill\"><img src=\"{{ 'movaro-about2.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=320\" srcset=\"{{ 'movaro-about2.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=160 160w, {{ 'movaro-about2.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=320 320w\" sizes=\"150px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"bt\"><h3>Finally — do it solo<\/h3>\n        <p>If trimming your cat has always been a two-person job, this is the part that changes your week. Wrapped and calm, your cat simply stays put — so one person, one pair of hands, gets it done in <b class=\"hl\">a few quiet minutes.<\/b> No more begging a friend to come over. No more giving up halfway.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"proof\">● Made for solo owners &amp; one-handed care<\/span><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"brow reveal\">\n      <div class=\"ill\"><img src=\"{{ 'movaro-about3.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=320\" srcset=\"{{ 'movaro-about3.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=160 160w, {{ 'movaro-about3.jpg' | asset_url }}&width=320 320w\" sizes=\"150px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"bt\"><h3>Pays for itself in ~3 trims<\/h3>\n        <p>A groomer charges $25–$30 a trim. A sedated vet visit runs $145–$500 — every single time. The Movaro wrap is a one-time $64.99 and <span class=\"hl\">pays for itself in about three trims<\/span>, then keeps saving you for years of nails, meds and grooming you do calmly at home.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"proof\">● One wrap ≈ 3 trims — then it's saving you money<\/span><\/div>\n    <\/div><\/div><\/div>",
