s=\"mc-tile\"><div class=\"mc-ill\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M20 14 h16 a6 6 0 0 1 6 6 v24 a6 6 0 0 1 -6 6 h-16 a6 6 0 0 1 -6 -6 V20 a6 6 0 0 1 6 -6Z\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#3E5C5A\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"\/><circle cx=\"48\" cy=\"33\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#C8BAA3\" stroke=\"#3E5C5A\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"\/><path d=\"M44.5 30 v-3 M48 29 v-3 M51.5 30 v-3\" stroke=\"#3E5C5A\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"\/><\/svg><\/div><div class=\"mc-cap\">One limb out<small>quick — never cornered<\/small><\/div><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"mech-pts reveal\">\n      <details class=\"mpt\"><summary><b>Deep-pressure calm<\/b><span>Even pressure tells the nervous system \"you're safe\" — the fight drains out.<\/span><i class=\"ch\">+<\/i><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">A cheap bag presses nowhere and grips everywhere, so the cat keeps struggling. Even, all-over pressure is the same \"swaddle\" response that settles a baby.<\/div><\/details>\n      <details class=\"mpt\"><summary><b>Less to panic about<\/b><span>Soft, quiet fabric removes the noise &amp; visual chaos that set a cat off.<\/span><i class=\"ch\">+<\/i><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">No scary plastic crinkle, nothing flapping — calmer input means a calmer cat from the very first second.<\/div><\/details>\n      <details class=\"mpt\"><summary><b>One limb, then done<\/b><span>Expose only the paw you need — quick, and never fully cornered.<\/span><i class=\"ch\">+<\/i><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">You work one area at a time instead of pinning the whole cat, so it's fast and far less stressful for both of you.<\/div><\/details>\n    <\/div><\/div><\/div><script>(function(){function o(){if(matchMedia('(min-width:990px)').matches)document.querySelectorAll('.mech-d .mpt').forEach(function(d){d.open=true});}if(document.readyState==='loading')document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',o);else o();})();<\/script>",
