    "faq": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{{ 'movaro-product.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}\n<div class=\"mvb bg-paper\"><div class=\"mvb-sec faq\">\n    <div class=\"sect-head reveal\"><div class=\"eyebrow\">Simple, honest answers<\/div><h2>Questions, answered<\/h2><\/div>\n    <details open><summary>\"This would never work on MY cat.\" <span class=\"pm\">+<\/span><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">That's what most owners say — including the ones reviewing the spiciest, most fractious cats they've owned. The swaddle pressure works <i>with<\/i> a cat's instinct to feel safe when held snugly, not against it. And you're covered by our 30-day guarantee, so trying it on your cat costs you nothing.<\/div><\/details>\n    <details><summary>Isn't wrapping cruel? Won't it panic more? <span class=\"pm\">+<\/span><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">Gentle wrapping is the opposite of scruffing — vets use it precisely because it calms. The fabric is soft and quiet (no scary plastic), it lowers visual stimulation, and most cats settle within a minute. We include a positive-association quick-start so the very first time builds trust instead of fear.<\/div><\/details>\n    <details><summary>What size do I need? <span class=\"pm\">+<\/span><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">We make Kitten, S, M, L and XL — most adult cats are M, large or fluffy cats L\/XL. Our size finder matches by weight and build. (The #1 complaint with other wraps is one-size-fits-all; we fixed that.)<\/div><\/details>\n    <details><summary>Can I use it with meds my vet prescribed? <span class=\"pm\">+<\/span><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">Yes — owners use it for pills, ear drops, subQ fluids and insulin, and it works alongside calming aids like gabapentin your vet may already recommend. It simply makes home care easier. It's a grooming &amp; calming aid, not a medical device.<\/div><\/details>\n    <details><summary>What if it doesn't work for us? <span class=\"pm\">+<\/span><\/summary><div class=\"ans\">Send it back within 30 days for a full refund — and keep the guide as our gift. Free US shipping. That's the Calm Guarantee: the only risk is staying stuck with nail-day battles.<\/div><\/details>\n  <\/div><\/div>",
